<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Otto Heyden</head><p>Der Rat lädt Heyden für kommenden Freitag vor.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_524" id="261v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_524_r2l27">Otten Heyden </ab>
</del></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_524_r2l28">Vnſer
                                    <expan>fr<ex>euntschaft</ex></expan> beuor
                                    <expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> Ott / <del rend="strikethrough">
                                VVir </del> Als du vnd <del rend="strikethrough">Sebo </del>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l29">Volkmeir vnſer <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd
                            Ratgeſell <expan>miteinand<ex>er</ex></expan> herab ge - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l30">ſcheẏden ſeit / Alſo laſʒ niht du kumſt cʒu vns
                            herein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l31">daʒ du auf den nehſten freẏtag hie von vns ſeiſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l32"><expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> der leuterer vnſer
                            diener auch auf <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l33">kumen ſol / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
</ab>
</del>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_524" id="261v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Otten Heyden </del></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Unser <expan>fr<ex>euntschaft</ex></expan> bevor.
                                    <expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Ott, als du und
                                    <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Volkmeir, unser
                                    <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und ratgesell,
                                    <expan>miteinand<ex>er</ex></expan> herab gescheyden seit, also
                        lasz niht, du kumst czu uns herein, daz du <app><note><q type="date">auf den nehsten freytag</q>In Frage kommen 23./30.09./07./14./21.10.1412</note></app> hie
                            von uns seist. <expan>Wan<ex>n</ex></expan> der Leuterer, unser diener,
                            auch auf <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czeit kumen sol.
                                    <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex>.</expan></del></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
